@startuml
title Strategy

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Encapsulate interchangeable algorithms; let them vary independently from clients.

**Use when**: Choose algorithm at runtime; avoid conditional logic.

**Key participants**: Context, Strategy, ConcreteStrategy.
endlegend

class Context {
  -strategy : Strategy
  +setStrategy(s: Strategy)
  +execute()
}

interface Strategy {
  +doAlgorithm()
}

class ConcreteStrategyA
class ConcreteStrategyB

Strategy <|.. ConcreteStrategyA
Strategy <|.. ConcreteStrategyB
Context o-- Strategy
@enduml